formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) The project land situated at Sub Plot No. 2, Survey No. 41, F.P. No. 55, Moje Hanspura, Ahmedabad on which Adhishthan Bungalow  is being developed on Phase-II , whereas Phase-I was developed having Project Name-Shantikunj and registered with Guj RERA vide Registration No. PR/GJ/AHMEDABAD/AHMEDABAD/AUDA/RAA01034/161217. The promoter has absorbed entire cost of land including stamp duty and Plan Fees / FSI payment in Phase-I project instead of allocating proportionate cost of land in Phase-I and Phase-II on the basis of land area of respective Phase.  Accordingly, land cost incurred and paid for Phase-II (Adhishthan Bungalow) is restated as Nil in Form- 3 to the extent it is claimed in Phase-I to derive actual withdrawal limit from designated RERA account of the Phase-II project (Adhishthan Bungalow). However, it is further clarified that the promoter has made full payment to the land owners.

2) Balance of outstanding loans as reported in details of project loans and lenders are inclusive of interest thereon.
